adept.common
Class ScriptVariable

java.lang.Object
  adept.common.Item
      adept.common.HltContent
          adept.common.ScriptVariable

public final class ScriptVariable
extends HltContent

A variable in an event script. For example, in a criminal justice event, there would probably be separate variables for the criminal, the victim, the prosecutor, etc. These variables may then appear in multiple ScriptEventArguments. All script-related classes are "locally immutable" so long as the IType implementation used is. However, they all inherit from the mutable HltContent class, whose associated fields are mutable. The Object.hashCode() and Object.equals(Object) implementations are the default.
